---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Formula from '../components/Formula.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="论文书桌 | 松间笔记" description="硕士论文：具双奇性的拟抛物方程的局部适定性与稳态解。这里不放 PDF，而是把论文拆成可阅读的研究笔记。" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="page-main">
			<section class="page-hero paper-card">
				<p class="eyebrow">Thesis Desk</p>
				<h1>论文书桌</h1>
				<p class="page-lead">
					论文标题：<strong>具双奇性的拟抛物方程的局部适定性与稳态解</strong>。这里不提供 PDF 下载，而是把论文拆成若干可阅读的研究笔记：模型从哪里来、困难在哪里、证明路线如何展开，以及数值例子如何帮助理解。
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="hub-section">
				<div class="hub-card main-card paper-card">
					<span class="hub-badge">研究对象</span>
					<h2>双奇异权拟抛物方程</h2>
					<div class="equation-box">
						<Formula math="\\begin{cases} |x|^{-s_1}u_t-\\Delta u_t-\\Delta u = |x|^{-s_2}|u|^{p-2}u, & (x,t)\\in \\Omega\\times(0,T),\\\\ u(x,0)=u_0(x), & x\\in\\Omega,\\\\ u(x,t)=0, & (x,t)\\in\\partial\\Omega\\times(0,T). \\end{cases}" displayMode={true} />
					</div>
					<p>
						演化项和源项各带一个独立的奇异权 <code>|x|<sup>&minus;s<sub>1</sub></sup></code> 和 <code>|x|<sup>&minus;s<sub>2</sub></sup></code>。研究方法分为两条主线：发展方程的局部适定性和稳态方程的非平凡解存在性。
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="hub-grid">
					<div class="hub-card paper-card">
						<span class="hub-badge">主线一</span>
						<h2>局部解</h2>
						<p class="hub-path">截断 → Galerkin → Hardy&ndash;Sobolev → Banach 不动点 → 爆破判据</p>
						<p>证明初边值问题在某个时间区间内存在唯一弱解，并建立最大存在时间有限时的爆破判据。</p>
						<div class="hub-links">
							<a href="/blog/local-solution-proof/">→ 局部解证明地图</a>
							<a href="/blog/why-galerkin/">→ Galerkin 方法在做什么</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="hub-card paper-card">
						<span class="hub-badge">主线二</span>
						<h2>稳态解</h2>
						<p class="hub-path">能量泛函 → Mountain Pass → Palais&ndash;Smale → Nehari</p>
						<p>证明对应椭圆方程存在非平凡弱解，使用变分法和山路定理。</p>
						<div class="hub-links">
							<a href="/blog/mountain-pass-steady-state/">→ 稳态解变分方法</a>
							<a href="/blog/why-mountain-pass/">→ 为什么像翻过一座山</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="chapter-overview paper-card">
				<h2>从哪里开始读</h2>
				<div class="reading-guide">
					<div class="guide-item">
						<span class="guide-icon">&#9670;</span>
						<div>
							<strong>想快速知道研究什么</strong>
							<p><a href="/blog/double-singular-pseudo-parabolic/">拟抛物方程研究框架</a> — 方程全景、参数条件来源、两条主线总览。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="guide-item">
						<span class="guide-icon">&#9670;</span>
						<div>
							<strong>想理解局部解</strong>
							<p><a href="/blog/local-solution-proof/">局部解证明地图</a>、<a href="/blog/why-galerkin/">Galerkin 方法在做什么</a>、<a href="/blog/galerkin-method-notes/">Galerkin 方法学习笔记</a>。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="guide-item">
						<span class="guide-icon">&#9670;</span>
						<div>
							<strong>想理解稳态解</strong>
							<p><a href="/blog/mountain-pass-steady-state/">稳态解变分方法</a>、<a href="/blog/why-mountain-pass/">为什么像翻过一座山</a>。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="guide-item">
						<span class="guide-icon">&#9670;</span>
						<div>
							<strong>想看直观例子</strong>
							<p><a href="/blog/numerical-glimpse/">数值实验只是直观</a> — 参数实例、Mountain Pass 路径可视化、半离散演化实验。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="guide-item">
						<span class="guide-icon">&#9670;</span>
						<div>
							<strong>想了解模型背景</strong>
							<p><a href="/blog/singular-weights-physical-picture/">奇异权到底是什么意思</a>、<a href="/blog/from-ode-to-double-singular/">从一个数的变化到双奇异权拟抛物方程</a>。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="chapter-overview paper-card">
				<h2>全文结构</h2>
				<div class="chapter-list">
					<div class="chapter-item">
						<span class="chapter-num">第 1 章</span>
						<span class="chapter-name">绪论</span>
						<span class="chapter-desc">研究背景、方程模型、参数条件推导、文献综述、主要工作与创新点</span>
					</div>
					<div class="chapter-item">
						<span class="chapter-num">第 2 章</span>
						<span class="chapter-name">预备知识</span>
						<span class="chapter-desc">L<sup>p</sup> 空间、Sobolev 空间、变分法框架、Hardy&ndash;Sobolev 不等式与加权紧嵌入</span>
					</div>
					<div class="chapter-item">
						<span class="chapter-num">第 3 章</span>
						<span class="chapter-name">局部解</span>
						<span class="chapter-desc">截断处理 → Galerkin 逼近 → 先验估计 → 不动点方法 → 半群替代证明 → 爆破判据</span>
					</div>
					<div class="chapter-item">
						<span class="chapter-num">第 4 章</span>
						<span class="chapter-name">稳态解的存在性</span>
						<span class="chapter-desc">能量泛函构造 → C<sup>1</sup> 与 PS 条件验证 → Mountain Pass → Nehari 最小化</span>
					</div>
					<div class="chapter-item">
						<span class="chapter-num">第 5 章</span>
						<span class="chapter-name">实例分析与计算验证</span>
						<span class="chapter-desc">三维单位球参数实例、物理含义、Mountain Pass 能量路径可视化、径向半离散数值实验</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="chapter-overview paper-card">
				<h2>三个核心方法</h2>
				<div class="method-grid">
					<div class="method-item">
						<h3>Galerkin 方法</h3>
						<p>将无穷维 PDE 投影到有限维空间，建立与维数无关的估计，通过弱收敛和紧性工具取极限。</p>
					</div>
					<div class="method-item">
						<h3>变分法 / Mountain Pass</h3>
						<p>将稳态解视为能量泛函的临界点，利用山路几何结构和 PS 条件证明非平凡解的存在性。</p>
					</div>
					<div class="method-item">
						<h3>Hardy&ndash;Sobolev 不等式</h3>
						<p>处理奇异权重带来的积分控制问题，是连接加权空间、紧嵌入和能量估计的核心不等式。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="back-note">
				<p>相关页面：<a href="/math">数学一隅</a> · <a href="/physics">物理回声</a> · <a href="/blog">笔记集合</a> · <a href="/projects">项目小径</a></p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	.page-main {
		padding-top: 4rem;
	}

	.page-hero {
		padding: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.page-hero h1 {
		font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.page-lead {
		max-width: 44rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.hub-section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hub-card {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.hub-card h2 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
	}

	.hub-card p {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.96rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
	}

	.hub-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--leaf);
		border-radius: 4px;
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.hub-path {
		font-family: "Atkinson", sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.88rem !important;
		color: var(--leaf) !important;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
	}

	.hub-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.hub-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		padding-top: 0.4rem;
	}

	.hub-links a {
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.hub-links a:hover {
		color: var(--twig);
	}

	.equation-box {
		margin: 0.8rem 0;
		padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
		border-radius: 6px;
		background: rgba(255, 253, 247, 0.55);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		overflow-x: auto;
	}

	.chapter-overview {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.chapter-overview h2 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
	}

	.chapter-list {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.chapter-item {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 5.5rem 8rem 1fr;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		padding: 0.6rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
		align-items: baseline;
	}

	.chapter-item:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.chapter-num {
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.chapter-name {
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--ink);
		font-size: 0.96rem;
	}

	.chapter-desc {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.reading-guide {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.8rem;
	}

	.guide-item {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5rem 1fr;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		padding: 0.6rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
		align-items: baseline;
	}

	.guide-item:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.guide-icon {
		color: var(--leaf);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1;
		padding-top: 0.3rem;
	}

	.guide-item p {
		margin: 0.15rem 0 0;
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.guide-item a {
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
	}

	.method-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.method-item {
		padding: 0.8rem 0;
	}

	.method-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
	}

	.method-item p {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.back-note {
		padding-top: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--soft-muted);
		font-size: 0.94rem;
	}

	.back-note a {
		color: var(--leaf-dark);
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.page-main {
			padding-top: 2rem;
		}

		.page-hero {
			padding: 1.25rem;
		}

		.page-hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.6rem;
		}

		.hub-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.chapter-item {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 0.2rem;
		}

		.method-grid,
		.guide-item {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
